{"type": "article", "id": 20757, "title": "儿童护肤品包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-15T07:17:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606003333NjbKSMdWI2EB3HTe.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一组儿童使用的清洁用品系列，来自法国平面设计师 Luc Borho 。他们想要优雅而带着童真的设计，同时兼具化妆品的严谨可靠。乳白色的背景上简单画出了蓝色和肉色的圆圈，还留有深浅的笔触。虽然没有特别的含义，却有着儿童画一样的简单而活泼。这一系列的外形都是普通化妆品的样式，以此来体现化妆品的本质。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003331TJCvKf8mSi9FERrx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.92379182\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003331UAMYo85Czx2u1piF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.09479554\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003332vlFXcUKrz0df1ERm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.44423792\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606003332FwlJT25nsaLRc7tq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.34944238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}